        " نِعْمَ الْعَوْنُ الدُّنْيَا عَلَى طَلَبِ الْآخِرَةِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, form Ali Bin Al Hakam, from Ali Al Ahmasy, from a man, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The best of the assistance is the world, upon the seeking of the Hereafter’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "14. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad from Ali ibn al-Hakam from Ali al-Ahmasiy from a man who has said the following: “Abu Ja’far, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘The worldly help in one’s quest for success in the hereafter is the best help.’” "
        ]
      }
